<book>
    <name>Oyster Soup</name>
    <author>Eric Lease Morgan</author>
    <copyright holder="Eric Lease Morgan">copy; 2003</copyright>
<ingredients>
    <list>
        <item>Stalk of celery</item>
        <item>onion</item>
        <item>tablespoon of butter</item>
        <item>Cups of oyster and their liquor</item>
        <item>Cups of half and half</item>
    </list>
</ingredients>
<process>
    <p>Begin by sautening the celery and onions in butter until soft.</p>
    <p>Add oysters, oyster liquor and cream</p>
    <p>Heat until de oysters float</p>
    <p>Serve in warm bowls</p>
    <p>Yummy!</p>
</process>
</book>